tafsir[176]{c,v,t}:
  4,1,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e, hulee Joomi mon, ko KaЕ‹ko Woni TagirЙ—o on e woЕ‹kii wooti ; ko woni ben mon Aadama, O Tagi immorde e Aadama sonna makko Hawwaa' yumma on, O Saaki immorde e Й“en Й—iЙ—o nder leydi ndin yimЙ“e Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e ; worbe e rewЙ“e. Hulee Alla on Mo yoga mon tororta yoya tuma ontigi wi'ata : ""Mi torike ma fii Alla waЙ—am huunde kaari"". Hulee taЖґugol enЙ—ammaaje Й—en humindirЙ—e on. Pellet, Alla Laatike e dow mooЙ—on Deeno ; hay huunde e golle mon Й—en laawotaako Mo, O MoftayЙ—e fow O YoЙ“ita on Й—e."
  4,2,"Onon kaliifaaЙ“e, jonnitee alyatiimaaЙ“e Й“en jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no timmiri si Й“e hellifaama, wata on waЙ—titir haraamu on ko dagii ; ko Й—um woni Жґettugol jawle maЙ“Й“e laaЙ“uЙ—e Й—en jillindiron e jawle mon Й—en, wata on huuwu Й—um ; pellet, huuwugol Й—um laatike bakkaatu mawЙ—o ka Alla."
  4,3,"Si on hulii roЕ‹kugol nunЙ—ude alyatiimaaЙ“e Й“en tammbitiЙ—on si on resii Й“e, wano hulugol wata on roЕ‹ku timminnde teЕ‹e maЙ“Й“e Й—en maa bonagol e maЙ“Й“e, haray tertee Й“e reson Й“en laaЙ“uЙ“e e sonnaaЙ“e goo ko woori Й“e, si Й—on yiЙ—i on resay Й—iЙ—o maa tato maa nayo. Si on hulii nde roЕ‹koton nunЙ—ude hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, haray resee gooto maa dakmitoron Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Г±aame mooЙ—on ; tawde wonaa ko waЙ—Й—anii kon Й“eya sonnaaЙ“e e haqqeeji waЙ—Й—ii Й“en Й—on. Ko jaЕ‹taa koo e oo Aaya fii fiyaake alyatiimaaЙ“e Й“en e yonndinorgol sonnaajo gooto maa dakmitora horЙ“e Й“en, Й“uri Й“aЙ—taade on nde on ooГ±o."
  4,4,"Jonnitiree rewЙ“e Й“en teЕ‹e Й—en dokkal waЙ—Й—ingal. Si Й“e anniyoranike on woЕ‹kiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in goЙ—Й—um e Й—en teЕ‹e ko aldaa e waawneede, haray Г±aamee Й—um, no newanii on laaЙ“ani on."
  4,5,"Onon fewjooЙ“e, wata on jonnu jawle Й—en on mo waawaa firlitaade fii majje, Й—en jawle, Alla WaЙ—iranii on Й—e dartorЙ—e nguurdam e fiyakuuji jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, Й“ee Й—oo non hanndaa e kippugol reena jawle. Г‘amminee e majje holtinon Й“e, wowlanon Й“e konngol moЖґЖґol, fodon Й“e no moЖґЖґiri wonnde on jonnitayЙ“e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en si Й“e hellifaama."
  4,6,"Onon fewjooЙ“e, jarribee alyatiimaaЙ“e Й“en si Й“e hellifaama, jonnonЙ“e seeЙ—a e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й“e haajitora, si Й“e haajitoriiЙ—e no haaniri, feeГ±anii on wonnde Й“e ЖґoЖґii ; haray jonnitee Й“e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en no timmiri.Wata on Г±aamir jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en fantingol Й“uri ko Alla Daginani on haajitorgol e majje, wata on yaccor Г±aamugol Й—e fii wata Й“e hellife Й“e henndooЙ—e. Kala e mon tawЙ—o ko jogiiЙ—o jawdi, yo o haЙ—ito Жґettugol jawdi alyatiima. Kala e mon kadi tawЙ—o ko waasiraaЙ—o jawdi, yo o haajitor yeru makko on. Si Й“e hellifaama on jonnitiiЙ“e jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, seedinee e kon ko jonnitoton fii reenugol haqqeeji Й—in e fii wata on lurru. Alla Yonii SeediiЙ—o e Й—um, Hasboowo jeyaaЙ“e Й“en e golle maЙ“Й“e."
  4,7,"Hino woodani worЙ“e Й“en : geЙ“al immorde e kon ko neene e baaba e Й“adiiЙ“e ngacci ko; wano banndi- raaЙ“e Й“en maa kaawu e bappa e baaba en mawЙ—o, si wonii Й“e faatike, Й—uuЙ—i famЙ—i e ko Й“e acci kon. Hino woodani kadi rewЙ“e Й“en : geЙ“al immorde e kon ko Й“en Й—on acci ; Й“e haanaa Й—awireede Й—um wano majjunooЙ“e Й—awiraynoo rewЙ“e e paykoy ka ndonndi. Ngal geЙ“al ko haqqee maЙ“Й“e Й“annginaaЙ—o emmbere mun, ngal Alla ToowuЙ—o On Farli."
  4,8,"Si Й“en Й“e ronataa tawaama ka senndoore ; wano Й“adondiral en maa alyatiima en maa waasuЙ“e Й“en, okkoreeЙ“e e ndin jawdi ndi senndoton yeru ko waalanii woЕ‹kii mon, Й“en ko hatonjimЙ“e e Й—um, wowlanon Й“e haala moЖґЖґuka."
  4,9,"Yo hulu Й“en Й“e tawata si Й“e maayii Й“e accii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e paykoy tokosoy lo'ukoy, Й“e hulanay koy yeebagol, yo Й“e hulu Alla e Й“en alyatimeeЙ“e Й“e Й“e halfinaa Й“e Й—ala tooГ±ugol Й“e fii no Alla Newinirana Й“e heЙ“ugol ko moЖґЖґoo e fayЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wano Й“e moЖґЖґori non e Й“eya fayЙ“e, yo Й“e moЖґЖґo e Й“en fayЙ“e Й“e yewta Й“e konngol sawaaba=peewngol, Й“e jonnita Й“e haqqeeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka ndonndi, Й“e waasa haЙ—de ko*e mu*en moЖґЖґere tammbitagol Й“e ngol."
  4,10,"Pellet, Й“en ЖґettooЙ“e jawle alyatiima en Й“e funsiraЙ—e(pirlitoo heen) tooГ±e e jaggitere, pellet ko Й“e woni naadude kon ka deedi maЙ“Й“e ko yiite huЙ“Й“aynge e maЙ“Й“e, yiite ngen sunnoyayЙ“e Г‘alnde Darngal."
  4,11,"Alla no aadani no yamirde on e fii ndonndi Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, wonnde ndonndi ndin senndirte hakkunde maЙ“Й“e wano nii : Й“iЙ—Й—o gorko on heЙ“a geЙ“al rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Si maayuЙ—o on accii Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e tun, hino woodani rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Й“en haa ko Й“uri Й—on, tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i e ko maayЙ—o on acci kon. Si tawii non ko jiwo gooto, hino woodani mo feccere ndonndi ndin. Hino woodani neene e baaba maayЙ—o on gooto kala e maЙ“Й“e, jeegaЙ“al ko o acci kon ; si tawii himo jogii Й“iЙ—Й—o (woni gorko maa jiwo), si o jogaaki non Й“iЙ—Й—o o maraa kadi ronooЙ“e si wanaa ben makko e neene makko en, hino woodani neene makko tataЙ“al, ben makko Жґetta ko heddii kon e ndonndi ndin. Si maayЙ—o on no jogii neene-gootooЙ“e maa baaba-gootooЙ“e Й—iЙ—o maa ko Й“uri, Й“e laatii worЙ“e maa rewЙ“e, haray no woodani neene makko jeegaЙ“al farlaangal, ko heddii kon jonnee ben makko, neene-gootooЙ“e Й“en maa baaba-gootooЙ“e Й“en heЙ“ataa hay huunde. Ndee senndoore ndondu, ko Й“aawo siinugol wasiyee mo maayЙ—o on wasiyinoo, sarti hara on wasiyee Й“urataa tataЙ“al jawdi makko ndin, e sarti kadi yoЙ“itugol Г±amaale makko Й—en. GomЙ—ii Alla WaЙ—irii non senndugol ndonndi ndin, tawde on anndaa hakkunde e baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ko hombo e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri Й“adoraade on nafa aduna e laakara ; maayЙ—o on hino sikka goЙ—Й—o goo moЖґЖґere, o Жґetta jawdi makko ndin fow o hunoo on Й—on, maa o sikka ontigi ko boni, o Й—awa mo ndi, hino wona kadi liddu Й—um. Ko Alla Tun Anndi ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude e Й—um, hay huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo ; ko Й—um waЙ—i si O Senndiri ndonndi ndin no O ЖЃannginiri non, O WaЙ—i Й—um farilla mo O WaЙ—Й—ini e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu mo huunde suuЙ—otaako Mo e moЖґЖґere jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e sari'a Makko on e toppitagol Makko ngol."
  4,12,"Hino woodani on onon resuЙ“e, feccere e ko rewЙ“e mon acci, si tawii Й“e jogaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o woni gorko maa debbo, woni ko onon Й“e jibinani maa gorko goo Si tawii hiЙ“e jogii Й“iЙ—Й—o woni gorko maa debbo, hino woodani on nayaЙ“al e kon ko Й“a acci e jawdi ; ko yo on senndane Й—um Й“aawo nde wasiyee maЙ“Й“e on siineede Г±amaale maЙ“Й“e Й—en yoЙ“itee. Hino woodani kadi resaaЙ“e mon Й“en, nayaЙ“al e ko accuЙ—on kon, si tawii on jogaaki Й“iЙ—Й—o -woni gorko maa debbo, woni Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e maa Й“iЙ—Й“e gorko goo. Si tawii hiЙ—on jogii Й“iЙ—Й—o -woni gorko maa debbo, hino woodani Й“e jeetataЙ“al e ko accuЙ—on kon ; Й“e senndaЕ‹te Й—um Й“aawo nde wasiyee mon on siineede Г±amaale mon Й—en yoЙ“itee. Si gorko maayii o jogitaaki mawЙ“e maa Й“iЙ—Й—o, maa debbo si maayii o jogitaaki mawЙ“e maa Й“iЙ—Й—o, kono hara on maayЙ—o hino jogitii neene-gooto gorko maa debbo ; hino woodani e Й“en neene-gootooЙ“e makko jeegaЙ“al farlaangal, si tawii non Й“en neene-gootooЙ“e makko worЙ“e maa rewЙ“e hino Й—uuЙ—i ; haray hino woodani Й“e denndaangal kafugol tataЙ“al farlaangal, rewЙ“e e worЙ“e maЙ“Й“e fotay e maggal, ko woni tun, Й“e henndike geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal woo Й“aawo nde wasiyee maayЙ—o on siineede Г±amaale makko Й—en yoЙ“itee, e sarti hara on wasiyee wonaa lorroowo ronooЙ“e Й“en ; wano wasiyorgol ko Й“uri tataЙ“al jawdi makko ndin. Ndee Г±aawoore nde wonnde e oo Aaya, ko Yamiroore nde Alla WaЙ—Й—ini e mooЙ—on. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko moЖґЖґani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en aduna e laakara, MuГ±Г±iiЙ—o Mo Hawjanaa lette yeddooЙ“e Й“en."
  4,13,"ЖЉen Г‘aawooje jaЕ‹taaЙ—e fii wonduЙ“e Й“en e woЙ—Й“e goo, ko Sari'aaji Alla Й—i O Sar'ini e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en fii yo Й“e gollitir. Kala on Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o gollitiri Yamirooje Makko Й—en o woЙ—Й—itii HaЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in, Alla Naadoyay mo Aljannaaji Й—i canЙ—i ilata doga ley kuЙ“eeji mun, ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder majji poomaa. Ko ndin njoЙ“di Joomiiko woni maloore mawnde nde sugu mun alaa."
  4,14,"Kala on yedduЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, o roЕ‹ki huutorde Г‘aawooje Makko Й—en maa o sikkitii Й—e, o jaggiti Keeri Makko Й—in, O Naadoyay mo yiite nge o Г±iiЙ“ata e muuЙ—um ; e kadi no woodani mo ton lept hoynooje."
  4,15,"ЖЃen waЙ—ooЙ“e paЕ‹kare jeenugol e rewЙ“e mon Й“en, woni laaЙ“uЙ“e maa ko woori Й—um, seedinee e maЙ“Й“e worЙ“e nayo juulЙ“e nunЙ—uЙ“e. Si Й“en seedike yi'ugol rewЙ“e Й“en no faggitoo paЕ‹kare Й—en, haray waЙ—iree leptugol Й“e ngol jogitagol ngol ka cuuЙ—i haa maayde nden arana Й“e, maa Alla WaЙ—ana Й“e laawol yawtirngol ko wanaa jogiteede nden ka cuuЙ—i. Refti Alla ЖЃanngini yaltirngal maЙ“Й“e ngal Й“aawo Й—um, O Sar'ini piyugol jiwo jeenuЙ—o mo jombaaka on sawru teemedere e raЙ—eede hitaande, rajmeede ware debbo jinuЙ—o jommbaaЙ—o on."
  4,16,"ЖЃen worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o faggitiiЙ“e paЕ‹kare jinaa Й—en, woni ko resЙ“e maa ko wonaa Й—um, leptireeЙ“e Й—emngal e junngo hoyniron Й“e Й—um. Si Й“e yiltike e on bone mo moЖґЖґini golle maЙ“Й“e, haray Й—uurnee e lorrugol Й“e ; sabu tuuuЙ—o e junuubi no wa'i wa on mo faggitaaki Й—um. Pellet, Alla Laatike JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en HinnotooЙ—o Й“e. Yonndinorgol ngol leptugol Й—on tun, ko aranun Farlanoo, refti Й—um Momtiraa piyugol mo jommbaa maa mo jommbaaka on raЙ—oo mo, woppa wara jomЙ“uЙ—o maa jommbaa."
  4,17,"Anndee ko Alla JaЙ“anta tuubuubuyee, ko Й“en faggitorayЙ“e goopi e geddi e dow majjere maЙ“Й“e bone Й—in geddi ; ko wano non kadi kala faggitorЙ—o goopi foti o tewi maa o tewaaki, hooti Й“e ruttiie Joomi maЙ“Й“e ado maayde nden ; Й“en Й—on, Alla JaЙ“anay Й“e tuubuubuyee, O Yawtana Й“e goopi maЙ“Й“e. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Makko ngol Sar'ina."
  4,18,"Alla JaЙ“ataa tuubuubuyee Й“en duumotooЙ“e e geddi Й“e roЕ‹ka tuubude e majji haa Й—eЙ—Й—ere maayde nannga Й“e, ontuma gooto e maЙ“Й“e wi'a : ""Min mi tuubii jooni e ko mi faggitii kon e geddi. Alla JaЙ“ataa fahin, tuubuubuyee Й“en maayidooЙ“e e keeferaaku. ЖЃen yeddooЙ“e duumo- tooЙ“e e geddi Й—on, e Й“en maayidooЙ“e e keeferaaku, Men Hebilanii Й“e fow lepte muusuЙ—e."
  4,19,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, dagaЕ‹taako on nde ronirton rewЙ“e baabiraaЙ“e mon e Й“adiiЙ“e mon wano jawdi ronirtee, maa etagol no resiraЙ“e maa no resinira Й“e on mo faalaЙ—on maa haЙ—on Й“e reseede. DagaЕ‹taako on kadi jogitorgol resaaЙ“e mon Й“en Й“e aГ±uЙ—on fii no lorriron Й“e haa Й“e jonnita on yoga e kon ko okkunoЙ—on Й“e e teЕ‹e maa ko nanndi heen si wanaa hara Й“e faggiti paЕ‹kare Й“annguЙ—o wano jinugol ; si Й“e huuwii Й—um, ina dagano on jogitorgol Й“e e Й“iЙ—tinana Й“e fii no Й“e soktitora kon ko okkunoЙ—on Й“e. Wonndiree e rewЙ“e mon Й“en no moЖґЖґiri, accon lorrugol Й“e, Й—uЙ—Й—inon moЖґЖґagol e maЙ“Й“e. Si on aГ±iriiЙ“e fiyaake aduna, muГ±Г±ee ; sabu no jortaa nde Alla WaЙ—ata e kon ko aГ±uЙ—on moЖґЖґere Й—uuЙ—unde aduna e laakara."
  4,20,"Si on faandike onon resuЙ“e, seerugol rewЙ“e mon Й“en, waЙ—titiron Й“e woЙ—Й“e goo, ella alaa e Й—um. Si tawii non on jonnii on debbo mo eЙ“Й“uЙ—on seerude jawl Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e fii teЕ‹e makko, dagaЕ‹taako on Жґettugol e Й—um hay huunde ; Жґettugol Й—um ko jeyaaЙ—um e fefindaande e bakkaat Й“annguЙ—o."
  4,21,"Ko honno Жґettirton kon ko okkuЙ—on Й“e e teЕ‹e Й“aawo nde yottindirЙ—on wirtondirЙ—on? Anndee fawГ±agol e ko Й“e jogitii kon Й“aawo Й—um, ko huunde Е‹iГ±aande.be nanngii e mon Ahdi cattudo, oon woni daganaade mon rewbe be tawa ko e Sariya Alla e Konngol mum."
  4,22,"Wata on jommbu Й“en Й“e baabiraaЙ“e mon Й“en jommbunoo ; Й—um no harmi si wanaa kon ko feЖґЖґi ado islaamu on, on nanngitirtaaake Й—um. Ko Й“iЙ—Й—o jommbata kon suddiiЙ—o ben mon, hino Е‹iГ±Г±aa ko tiiЙ—i, Alla no Tikkirana huuwuЙ—o Й—um, kadi ko laawol bonugol."
  4,23,"Alla Harminanii on resugol : NeeniraaЙ“e mon Й“en no Й“e foti waade ; wano neene neenemon maa pati mon ka neene maa pati mon ka baa, e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon rewЙ“e Й“en no foti waade ; Й—um ko wano Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“iЙ—Й—o mon debbo maa taaniraaЙ“e mon rewЙ“e, e Й“iЙ—Й“e jiwЙ“e Й“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon worЙ“e jibini maa Й“e Й“iЙ—Й“e mon rewЙ“e jibini no Й“e foti waade, banndiraaЙ“e mon rewЙ“e, e yaayiraaЙ“e mon maa yaayiraaЙ“e baabiraaЙ“e mon, e neeniraaЙ“e mon ka dewol maa neeniraaЙ“e baabiraaЙ“e mon ka dewol no Й“e foti waade, e jiwЙ“e [banndiraawo mon] neene-gooto maa baaba-gooto e jiwЙ“e neene-gooto maa baaba-gooto mon e Й“iЙ—Й“e Й“en Й—on no Й“e foti waade, e neeniraaЙ“e mon muynimЙ“e on, e banndiraaЙ“e mon rewЙ“e ka muynidal, e neeniraaЙ“e Й“eynguuli mon ; foti non on naatidii e maЙ“Й“e suudu maa hara on naatidaali e maЙ“Й“e suudu, e jiwЙ“e Й“eynguuli mon Й“e wanaa Й“iЙ—Й“e mon reedu ne'eteeЙ“e ko heewi kon ka galle mon ; hay si tawii non Й“e ne'aaka ka galle yonii tawde on naatidii e neene maЙ“Й“e en suudu, si tawii non on naatidaai e maЙ“Й“e suudu haray bakkaatu alanaa on nde resoton Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e rewЙ“e Й“en, hino harmani on kadi resugol Й“eynguuli Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en iwЙ“e e keeci mon ; hay si tawii non Й“e naatidaali e suudu, ko wano non kadi Й“eynguuli Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en ka muynidal, harminanaama on kadi hawtindirgol hakkunde banndiraaЙ“e Й—iЙ—o hawtuЙ“e enЙ—am maa muynidal ; si wanaa kon ko yawtunoo fewndo majjere, Alla Yaafike Й—um, pellet, Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko tuubooЙ“e Й“en ruttoo e Makko, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e. Tabitii kadi ka sunna, harmineede mooЙ“indirgol hakkunde debbo e yaayiraawo mun maa neenirawo makko ka dewol."
  4,24,"Harminanaama on kadi resugol : Й“en rewЙ“e jommbaaЙ“e ; si wanaa Й“en Й“e jeytirЙ—on Г±aame mon ka konehoyri fii laawol Alla, hino daganii on renndugol e Й“en Й—on tuma Й“e laaЙ“iri fiilordu. Alla Farlii Й—um e dow mooЙ—on, O Daginani on ko wanaa Й“en rewЙ“e Й—on, nde Й—aЙ“Й“irton laЙ“Й“ingol pittaali mon kon ko dagii hara wanaa faandagol jinaa. Kala mon dakmitorЙ—on e maЙ“Й“e desal, jonnee mo teЕ‹e makko Й—e Alla WaЙ—aniЙ“e Й—en farilla waЙ—Й—iiЙ—o on, bakkaatu alanaa on e kon ko yarlondirton Й—uytugol maa Й“eyda teЕ‹e waЙ—Й—iiЙ—e Й—en Й“aawo Й—um happeede. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o tagu Makko ngun, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e maЙ“Й“e, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Makko ngol e Sar'ia."
  4,25,"Kala e mon onon worЙ“e Й“en mo hattanaaka resugol rewЙ“e seЕ‹iiЙ“e sabu baasal yaajireede, hino daganoo mo resugol Й“en Й“e o jeytiri Г±aamo makko ngon ; si Й“en laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e. Ko Alla ЖЃuri Anndude haqiiqa gomЙ—inal mon e ko wirnii e fiyaake mon, onon e Й“en rewЙ“e, hiЙ—on fota ka diina e ka neЙ—Й—aaku, wata on towniЕ‹tinano resugol Й“en. ResireeЙ“e duЕ‹ayee mawЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, jonniron Й“e teЕ‹e maЙ“Й“e Й—en no haaniri ; si tawii ko Й“e laaЙ“uЙ“e hara wanaa feГ±Г±inooЙ“e jinnduru mun wanaa kadi njaatotooЙ“e fii ko jeenida e maЙ“Й“e. Si Й“e resaama, Й“e faggitike paЕ‹kare jinaa, foccireeЙ“e feccere paatawol rinЙ—umЙ“e Й“en : Й—um woni paatawol cappanЙ—e jowi, Й“e rajmetaake, ko rinЙ—uЙ“e Й“en piyetee haa maaya si Й“e jinii ko Й“e resaaЙ“e. Kon ko jaЕ‹taa Й—on e dagagol resude horЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e laaЙ“uЙ“e, ko hoynangol on hulanЙ—o hoore-mun yanugol e jinaa, fii o maraa feere resugol rinЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, wonnde muГ±Г±orgol desal horЙ“e Й“en Й“uri. Alla ko Haforanoowo kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e. No jeyaa e Hinnayee Makko on : Sar'inangol Й“e resugol horЙ“e Й“en tuma tawi feere alaa ko resira rinЙ—umЙ“e Й“e, fii hulugol jeeno."
  4,26,"Alla SeniiЙ—o On ko Faandorii Sar'ingol Й—ee Г±aawooje, ko ЖЃannginanngol on doose Diina Makko kan, e kon ko moЖґЖґinanta on aduna e laakara, Himo Faadori Й—um kadi Fewnirgol on laawi AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ado mon : ka dagingol harmina e ka jikkuuji maЙ“Й“e tedduuЙ—i, e fillayeeji maЙ“Й“e yettiniiЙ—i ; fii yo on Г±emtimЙ“e. Himo Faandii kadi ruttugol on e geddi adda on e Й—oftaare. Alla ko AnnduЙ—o moЖґЖґere jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Sari'aaji Makko e Toppitagol fiyakuuji maЙ“Й“e."
  4,27,"Alla no faandi JaЙ“angol on tuubuubuyee, O Yawtana on goopi mon, Й“en jokkuЙ“e mbeleendi mun hino faalaa nde woЙ—Й—itoron e laawol feewungol ngol woЙ—Й—itannde tiiЙ—unde."
  4,28,"Alla no YiЙ—i Hayfinanngol on e ko O Sar'inani on kon, O Fawataa on ko on hattatah ; tawde Himo Anndi lo'ere neЙ—Й—aЕ‹ke nden ka jikku e ka tagudi."
  4,29,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on yoga e mon Жґettir jawle yoga e hoore meh-re ; wano jattugol maa wujjugol maa ngeeynorgol ekn. Si wanaa hara ko jawle njulorЙ—e Й—e halduЙ“e welondiri e mun ; Й—en Й—on no dagoo Г±aamugol duncitora. Wata yoga mon waru yoga, wata goЙ—Й—o e mo'on kadi waru hoore-mun. Alla Laatike HinnotooЙ—o on ; HarminЙ—o ЖґiiЖґe mon e jawle mon e teddule mon."
  4,30,"Kala on huuwuЙ—o ko o haЙ—aa kon, o Г±aami jawle goЙ—Й—o maa o jaggitiri ontigi warugol mo ekn e hoore tewaare, aray Alla Naada mo yiite sunnaynge mo lepte mo Г‘alnde Darngal : Й—um ko ko newanii Alla ; sabu ko O HattanЙ—o kala huunde."
  4,31,"Onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, si on waЙ—Й—itike huuwugol bakkatuuji mawЙ—i Й—in ; wano kafidugol e Alla maa Жґagganngol jibimЙ“e Й—um maa ittugol woЕ‹kii maa Г±aamugol ribaa, Men Yawtanay on goopi mon tokoosi Й—in, Men Momtana on Й—i, Men Naada on e nokkuure teddunde ka Alla ; nden woni Aljanna."
  4,32,"Onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, wata on yelo ko Alla ЖЃurniri kon yoga mon dow yoga, sabu Й—um adday tikkere e ngaГ±aneendi. Haanaa ka rewЙ“e Й“en himmira kon ko Alla Hertinani worЙ“e Й“en, tawde kala maЙ“Й“e e geЙ“al mun. ЖЉaЙ“Й“iree Alla Й“eydaare e Dokke Makko. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde ; Himo Jonni kala ko hanndi kon e mun."
  4,33,"Wonannde kala e mooЙ—on Men WaЙ—anii Й—um heftuЙ“e ronooЙ“e kon ko jibimЙ“e Й“en e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en acci e ndonndi. ЖЃen Й“e fiЙ“odiЙ—on e mun woondooje mon Й—en e sabu moЖґЖґo : Jonnitee Й“en geЙ“al maЙ“Й“e ngal ka donal. Pellet, Alla Laatike ko O SeediiЙ—o e kala huunde ; hino jeyaa e mun, Seeditagol Mo nga'al ahodal mon. Ronindirgol e hoore woondoore ko gila ka fuЙ—Й—orde lislaamu fuЙ—Й—ii, Й—um momtaa ontuma."
  4,34,"WorЙ“e Й“en ko toppitotooЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“en, Й“e kippira Й“e sabu kon ko Alla Hertinani Й“e e ЖЃural Makko, e sabu kon ko O WaЙ—Й—ini e maЙ“Й“e nafqugol e rewЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Men rewЙ“e moЖґЖґuЙ“e : ko Й—oftotooЙ“e Joomi maЙ“Й“e On, Й“e yaЕ‹kinanoo moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, Й“e reenortooЙ“e ka moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wirnii peewal Alla. ЖЃen rewЙ“e Й“e huloton dartagol moodi maЙ“Й“e e konngol maa kuugal, fuЙ—Й—oree wurtugol Й“e ngol -onon moodiЙ“Й“e Й“en, anndiЕ‹tingol Й“e fii Alla, si Й“e wurtaaki, feron Й“e ka mbalndi ; saloЙ—on yottagol e maЙ“Й“e, si Й“e wurtaaki, piyon Й“e piggal ngal barmiЕ‹taa, si Й“e wurtike e Й—oftaare Alla nden, wata on jaggitir e maЙ“Й“e tooГ±e maa feloore. Pellet, Alla Laatike ToowuЙ—o e kala huunde, MawnuЙ—o e Jaati mun e Sifaaji mun, hulee Mo."
  4,35,"Si on hulii -onon Й“eynguureeji Й—in-, nde resindirЙ“e Й“en lurrata hakkunde maЙ“Й“e haa hewta ngayngu, hary imminee gorko nunЙ—uЙ—o immorЙ—o e yimЙ“e gorko on, e gorko nunЙ—uЙ—o immorЙ—o e yimЙ“e debbo on ; fii no Й“e Г±aawira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e no haaniri -foti Й“e seeday maa Й“e wontida- e hoore non ko woЕ‹tidugol ngol Й“uraa yiЙ—eede. Si Й“en Г±aawooЙ“e Й—iЙ—o faandike moЖґЖґingol, Alla Hawrindinay Й“e fottindingol hakkunde resondirЙ“e Й“en. Pellet, huunde suuЙ—aaki Alla e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, ko O AnnduЙ—o kala Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e soomi."
  4,36,"Rewee Alla Tun, hara on kafidaali e Makko goЙ—Й—um goo. MoЖґЖґon e jibimЙ“e on Й“en ; teddinon Й“e Й—oftoЙ—on Й“e, moЖґЖґoЙ—on e joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral Й“en, e alyatimeeЙ“e Й“en, e waasuЙ“e Й“en, moЖґЖґoЙ—on e kawtalo jom-Й“adondiral, e kawtaljo woЙ—Й—itiiЙ—o ka enЙ—am, moЖґЖґoЙ—on e wonndiiЙ—o on ka yahdu, moЖґЖґoЙ—on e seteejo tumaraЕ‹keejo, moЖґЖґoЙ—on e Й“en Й“e jeyruЙ—on Г±aame mon. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa on laatiiЙ—o Г±aaЖґoowo towniЕ‹tiniiЙ—o e yimЙ“e Й“en, mantoowo hoore-mun hakkunde yimЙ“e."
  4,37,"Alla YiЙ—aa Й“en haЙ—itotooЙ“e nafqugol kon ko O WaЙ—Й—ini e maЙ“Й“e immorde e ko O Arsike Й“e, hiЙ“e yamira woЙ—Й“e goo ko woori Й—um, hiЙ“e suuЙ—a kon ko Alla Okki Й“e e ЖЃural Makko : immorde e jawdi e ganndal ekn, hiЙ“e suuЙ—a yimЙ“e Й“en goonga kan, Й“e holla mehre nden ; Й—um fow ko jikkuuji keeferaaku, gomЙ—ii Alla Heblanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje."
  4,38,"Men Hebilanii kadi lepte Й—en Й“en funsirooЙ“e jawle mun Й—en yiinorgol yimЙ“e Й“en e yetteede e maЙ“Й“e, Й“en Й“e gomЙ—iЕ‹taa Alla, Й“e gomЙ—iЕ‹taa kadi Г‘alnde Darngal ; Men Maranii Й“en lepte hoynooje, ko jokkugol Й“e seytaane ngol woni ko majjini Й“e, kala non mo seytaane laatanii wondiЙ—Й—o ciЕ‹kodaaЙ—o : haray o bonii wondiЙ—Й—o!"
  4,39,"E ko honЙ—um lorraaynoo Й“e si Й“e gomЙ—inno Alla e Г‘alnde Darngal, Й“e nafqi e Й—en jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e fii Alla ? Si ko woni, moЖґЖґere nden ko e Й—um woni. Alla non Laatike AnnduЙ—o Й“e, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e fii maЙ“Й“e, O YoЙ“itoyay gooto kala e golle mun."
  4,40,"Pellet, Alla ToowuЙ—o On ko NunЙ—uЙ—o Mo tooГ±irtaa jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en hay huunde, O ЖЉuytataa moЖґЖґi maЙ“Й“e Й—in yeru Г±uungii, O ЖЃeydirtaa kadi bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e hay e huunde. Si wonii ko moЖґЖґere fotaynde abbere-jarra, O Sowiraynde ЖЃural Makko ngal, O Okka immorde ka Makko njoЙ“di mawndi baraaji."
  4,41,"Ko honno woniroyta muraadu ndu Г‘alnde Darngal tuma Men Addoyta Annabaajo immorde e kala mote mo no seeditoo e ko Й“e gollunoo, Men Addoye an NulaaЙ—o, e mofte maa Й—en ko a seeditotooЙ—o ?"
  4,42,"Nden Г‘alnde Mawnde, Й“en yedduЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on yeloto hara nun Й“e woЕ‹tayno leydi Й“e feppindinee e mayri, Й“e suuЙ—ataa Alla hay huunde e ko Й“e gollaynoo ; tawde Alla Sokoyay Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en fii wata Й“e wowlu, O DuЕ‹anoo (sakkita) tere maЙ“Й“e Й—en Й—e seeditoo golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  4,43,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on juulu hara hiЙ—on siwri haa Й—iwton e ngon siwrugol anndon ko wowloton -Й—um ko ado sanngara harminireede pellital - Wata on juulu kadi ko on modduЙ“e janaaba, wata on naatir non kadi ka juulirЙ—e si wanaa hara on feЖґЖґay woni haa lootoЙ—on. Si on woni e nawnraare haЙ—aynde on huutorgol ndiyam, maa hara ko on setiiЙ“e, maa goЙ—Й—o e mun yehi Й“aawo hoggo, maa hara on renndo e rewЙ“e Й“en ; roЕ‹kuЙ—on ndiyam, faandoree taamoragol leydi laaЙ“undi : mowlon geece mon Й—en e juuЙ—e mon Й—en. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo palje mon, Yawtanoowo on."
  4,44,"E a anndaa, an NulaaЙ—o, wonnde Й“ee alyahuudaaЙ“e Й“e Alla Okkunoo geЙ“al e ganndal Tawreetaare nden, hiЙ“e waЙ—titira peewal ngal majjere, hiЙ“e rerЙ—ira majjingol on onon muumini en, e laawol foccii ngol ngol NulaaЙ—o on addani on ; fii no jokkiron laawol maЙ“Й“e ooГ±ii ngol ngol ?!"
  4,45,"Ko Alla TedduЙ—o MawЙ—o On ЖЃuri Anndude ayЙ“e mon Й“en onon muumini en, O Humpitii on fii maЙ“Й“e O ЖЃannginni on ngayngu maЙ“Й“e ngun. Alla yonii GiЙ—o Reenoowo on, Alla yonii Ballo DaЙ—ndoowo mon pewje maЙ“Й“e e lorra maЙ“Й“e, O Wallay on e maЙ“Й“e."
  4,46,"Hino e Й“eya alyahuudaaЙ“e yimЙ“e waylirooЙ“e Konngol Alla Jippiingo ngol, Й“e waylira ngol ko ngol jippiniraaka, hiЙ“e wi'ana NulaaЙ—o on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun on, tuma on yamiri Й“e fiyaake : ""Men nanii haala maa kan, men yeddii yamiroore maa nden"", hiЙ“e jalkitira wi'ugol : ""HeЙ—ito ko men wi'aЕ‹te kon"" ; hiЙ“e heЙ“Й“itora haala maЙ“Й“e ""raa'inaa"" kan, faandorgol wiide : ""HeЙ—ito men"", si ko woni, ko ittugol yiila Й“e faandorii kon ko Й—emЙ—e maЙ“Й“e wowlata ; ko huЙ—ugol NulaaЙ—o on (yo o his) Й“e faanddii, e yuwugol ka diina. Hara nun Й“e wi'ayno : ""Men nanii haala maa kan, men Й—oftike yamiroore maa nden"", Й“e wi'a: ""HeЙ—ito"", hara Й“e wi'aali : ""A nanataa"", Й“e wi'a: ""HeЙ—ito men men gelloo haala maa"", Й“e tertoo wi'ugol : ""Aynu men"" ; ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖґЖґande Й“e, Й“ura kadi foccanaade Й“e ; sabu ko Й—on woni ne'anagol NulaaЙ—o on (yo o his). Ko woni tun, Alla HuЙ—ii Й“e, O Pottiniri Й“e e Yurmeende Makko nden sabu keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun, Й“e gomЙ—iЕ‹taa gomЙ—inal nafayngal."
  4,47,"Ko onon yo Й“eya okkanooЙ“e Defte imoorde e Alyahuuda e Annasaare, gomЙ—inee Nden nde Men Jippini e Muhammadu on mo jam e kisiyee woni e mun, Nden Deftere goonginnde ЖЉen wonЙ—e ka mon immorde e Tawreeta e Linjiila, ado Men Mehude momta tere Й—en ka geece mon, Men WaЙ—tira Й—e wano Й“abbe mon Й—en, maa Men WoЙ—Й—iЕ‹tina Й“e e Yurmeende Alla nden wano Men HuЙ—irnoo yimЙ“e asewe Й“en : jaggitunooЙ“e waaГ±ugol ngol nden Г±alnde haЙ—aande, Alla Wayliri Й“e BahЙ—i, Fiyaake Alla on e Kattal Makko ngal Laatike SiineteeЙ—um."
  4,48,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa gooto e tagu Makku ngun kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana on Mo O Muuyi geddi jaasuЙ—i sirku, Maa O Leptira Й—um nunЙ—al Makko ngal Mo O Muuyi e maЙ“Й“e yeru bakkaatu ontigi on. Kala non kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii haray o fefindike bakkaatu mawЙ—o mo yawtantaake."
  4,49,"E a anndaa an NulaaЙ—o, fiyaake Й“en laЙ“Й“inooЙ“e ko'e mun e golle mun ? Ko woni, ko Alla Tun woni LaЙ“Й“inoowo on Mo O Muuyi e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ; tawde ko KaЕ‹ko Anndi ko soomii e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e Й—uytaЕ‹taake huunde e baraaji golle maЙ“Й“e ; hay si fotii wa gaarahun tamaro."
  4,50,"Ndaarii NulaaЙ—o, hol no Й“e fefindorta e Alla fenaande tuma Й“e laЙ“Й“iЕ‹ta ko'e maЙ“Й“e ! ЖЉum Й—on yonii bakkaatu feeГ±Г±iЙ—o majjere maЙ“Й“e nden."
  4,51,"E hawnaali an NulaaЙ—o, fiyaake Alyahuuda Й“en okkanooЙ“e geЙ“al e ganndal, hiЙ“e gomЙ—ina Й—in reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e ko woori Alla, Й“e wi'ana yedduЙ“e Й“en : ""Ko Й“en Й“uri wonndiiЙ“e Muhammadu (saw) Й“en feewude laawol ?!""."
  4,52,"Ko Й“en wonnduЙ“e e nden fiЙ“nde bonnde woni ko Alla WoЙ—Й—indini e yurmeende Makko nden, kala non mo Alla HuЙ—i, a heЙ“ataa mo ballo."
  4,53,"ЖЃe alaa geЙ“al immorde e laamu, hara nun e heЙ“ayno ngal geЙ“al, Й“e okkataano goЙ—Й—o ko fotata hufol tamaroore ngun laamu."
  4,54,"Si ko woni, Й“e faala haasagol Muhammadu (saw) e wonndiiЙ“e makko Й“en dow kon ko Alla Okki Й“e immorde e Annabaaku e Liimanaaku e Г‘iiЙ“ugol ka leydi. Ko Й“e haasaЕ‹too Й“e ? GomЙ—ii Men Okkiino jurriya Ibraahiima on Deftere Jippinaande nden, e kon ko Men Wahyini e maЙ“Й“e ko jeyaaka e Deftere nden, Men Okki Й“e laamu yaajungu !."
  4,55,"Hino e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, on gomЙ—inЙ—o nden Jippinaande e Ibraahiima (yo o his) e AnnabaaЙ“e jeyaaЙ“e e jurriya makko on, hino e maЙ“Й“e kadi on Й—uurniiЙ—o e gomЙ—ingol nde, ko non kadi Й“ee Й—oo jogitori nden Jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his). Ko yiite ngen woni lepte kala yedduЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e."
  4,56,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en, aray ka Men NaadaЙ“e yiite Г‘alnde Darngal nge huuЙ“ita Й“e : tuma kala nge sunni guri maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Men WaЙ—titanay Й“e guri goЙ—Й—i fii no lepte Й—en duumora e maЙ“Й“e. Pellet, Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Mun e Г‘aawoore Mun."
  4,57,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe, aray ka Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Г‘alnde Darngal hino ila ley kuЙ“eeje majji canЙ—i, ko Й“e heddotooЙ“e ndeer ton poomaa, hino woodani Й“e ton Й“eynguuli laЙ“Й“inaaЙ—i e kala tuundi, Men Naadoyay Й“e dowЙ—i duumiindi ndi wulaa-Й“uuЙ“aa."
  4,58,"Pellet, Alla hino Yamira on nde Yottinton kala halfinaЙ—on e hoolaare faade e jeyЙ“e nde, Himo Yamira on kadi nunЙ—ugol tuma Г±aawoton hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en hara on ooГ±aaki e Г±aawoore nden. Pellet, ko Alla Waajorta on kon e kala huunde laamaa. Pellet, Alla Laatike Nanoowo haalaaji mon, ReenuЙ—o golle mon."
  4,59,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й—oftee Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, ciinon ko o yamiri e woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on haЙ—aaЙ—i makko, Й—oftoЙ—on kadi joomiraaЙ“e mon yamiroore Й“en fotde Й“e yamiraali on yeddugol Alla. Si on luutondirii e huunde, ruttee Й—aЙ“Й“ugol Г±aawoore mayre ka Deftere Alla e ka sunna Annabiijo Makko on (saw), si on laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden. Ko Й—um Й—on Й“uri moЖґЖґude e dii heddagol e lurral, ko Й—um kadi Й“uri labaneede on battane."
  4,60,"E a yi'aali an NullaЙ—o, lunndagol naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en ka Alyahuuda en, Й“en nodditorayЙ“e fenaande wiide hiЙ“e gomЙ—ini kon ko Jippinaa e ma'a e kon ko Jippinaa e NulaaЙ“e Й“en ado maaЙ—a ? HiЙ“e faandii Г±awitoroygol lurre maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko woori Saria Alla on, gomЙ—ii non Й“e yamiraama yeddugol Й—um. Seytaane hino faandii woЙ—Й—iЕ‹tingol Й“e e goonga kan fii wata Й“e feewi e makka."
  4,61,"Si naafiqi en Й“ee wi'anaama :"" Aree faade e kon ko Alla Jippini ka Deftere Makko immorde e Г±aawooje, e faade e NulaaЙ—o on fii no o Г±aawira hakkunde mo'on"", a yi'ay Й“e an NulaaЙ—o, hiЙ“e Й—uurnoo gaay e maaЙ—a Й“e Г±aawitora ko woori maa e falaade falagoltimmungol."
  4,62,"Ko honno naafiqi en wa'oyta tuma musiiba on memiroyta Й“e sabu kon ko Й“e faggitii e bone, refti Й“e ara e maa an NulaaЙ—o hiЙ“e ngantinoo woondira Alla : ""Men faandoraaki Г±aawitorgol ko woori NulaaЙ—o on si wanaa moЖґЖґinngol e hawrindinngol hakkunde luutondirЙ“e ?!"" Hara non ko e fenaande Й“e woni ; ko woni, moЖґЖґinngol, ko Г±aawirgol Sari'a Alla on e jeeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  4,63,"Ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla Anndi ko e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e soomi immorde e naafiqiyaagal e faandaare bonnde, terto Й“e an NulaaЙ—o, Й—uurnoЙ—aa gaay maЙ“Й“e, Й“annginanaaЙ“e Г‘aawoore Alla nden, wowlanaaЙ“e konngol tiiЙ—ungol yottotoongol e pittaali maЙ“Й“e."
  4,64,"Men Nuliraali NulaaЙ—o woo si wanaa fii yo o Й—ofte e kon ko yamirta e DuЕ‹ayee Alla e hoddireede mbo . Hara nun tuma Й“e tooГ±unoo pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e faggitii geddi, Й“e aruno ma an NulaaЙ—o, Й“e qirritii ko Й“e faggitii kon, Й“e nimsi, Й“e tuubi, Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“i ya'afuyee ka Alla, Й—aЙ“Й“anЙ—aa Й“e ya'afuyee ; Й“e tawayno Alla ko jaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  4,65,"Wonaa no naafiqi en aaЖґori non. Hooti Alla Woondirii Jaati Makko kin, wonnde Й“e gomЙ—iЕ‹taa gomЙ—inal sellungal fotde Й“e Г±aawitoraali ka NulaaЙ—o on fewndo nguurdam makko Й—am, Й“e Г±aawitora sari'a makko on Й“aawo faatagol makko ; tuma kala nde lurral yani hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, refti kadi Й“e weltora Г±aawoore NulaaЙ—o on, hara Й“e Й“iЙ—toraaki nde maa Й“e sikkitaaki, Й“e jebbilora nde hattirde e jebbilagol ko wirnii e ko feenyi."
  4,66,"Hara nun Men Farluno e maЙ“Й“e nde yoga maЙ“Й“e warata yoga, maa yaltugol e galleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ; ko seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e waЙ—aynoo Й—um. Yo Й“e yettude Alla tawnoo O Fawaali Й“e ko Й“e townataa. Sinno Й“e waЙ—uno ko Й“e yamiraa e Й—oftagol Alla, Й—um laatotono moЖґЖґere, e ko Й“urata tiiЙ—ude e tabital liimanaaku, Men YeЙ—ayno Й“e kadi baraaji mawЙ—i, Men Fewnira Й“e laawol Alla ngol e Aljanna Makko on :"
  4,67,"Hara nun Men Farluno e maЙ“Й“e nde yoga maЙ“Й“e warata yoga, maa yaltugol e galleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ; ko seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e waЙ—aynoo Й—um. Yo Й“e yettude Alla tawnoo O Fawaali Й“e ko Й“e townataa. Sinno Й“e waЙ—uno ko Й“e yamiraa e Й—oftagol Alla, Й—um laatotono moЖґЖґere, e ko Й“urata tiiЙ—ude e tabital liimanaaku, Men YeЙ—ayno Й“e kadi baraaji mawЙ—i, Men Fewnira Й“e laawol Alla ngol e Aljanna Makko on."
  4,68,"4:67"
  4,69,"Kala on Й—oftiiЙ—o Alla e NulaaЙ—o on : on Й—on wonndoyay e Й“en Й“e Alla Neeminiri naatugol Aljanna immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e, e goonguЙ“e e ko NulaaЙ“e Й“en addi kon Й“e gollitiri Й—um, e sahodinЙ“e fii laawol diina Alla, e moЖґЖґuЙ“e moЖґЖґini golle-mun. ЖЃen Й—on moЖґЖґii wonndiiЙ“e ka Aljanna !"
  4,70,"Ndin mbarjaari jaЕ‹taandi Й—on ko ЖЃural ngal Alla Hertinani jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Alla Yonii AnnduЙ—o fiyakuuji mon, O YoЙ“itoyay kala e golle mun !"
  4,71,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Жґettee reЕ‹torЙ—i mon Й—in jogitoЙ—on ko daЙ—itoron e ayЙ“e Й“en si hare yanii, yaltiron e maЙ“Й“e konu konu, maa yaltiron on denndaangal ; no gasiraЕ‹ta on woo mettinirangol ayЙ“e mon Й“en."
  4,72,"Hino e mo'on onon juulЙ“e Й“en, yimЙ“e nennotooЙ“e yahugol haЙ“a ayЙ“e mon Й“en sabu kulol reedu, Й“e nenna kadi woЙ“Й“e goo ; Й“en le ko naafiqi en. Si on waraama maa on foolaama, goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e weltora wi'ugol: ""GomЙ—ii Alla MoЖґЖґike e am, mi tawdaaka e maЙ“Й“e sakko musiiba heЙ“ida lam e maЙ“Й“e""."
  4,73,"Si tawii le ЖЃural foolugol maa heЙ“ugol honateeri heЙ“ii onon juulЙ“e Й“en immorde ka Alla, on nenniiЙ—o e jihaadi ndin wowliray wa si tawiino giggol laatanooki hakkunde mon e makko : ""Ee jalla am sinno mi laatoduno e maЙ“Й“e ka hare, mi heЙ“ii ЖЃural ngal Й“e heЙ“i !""."
  4,74,"Yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haЙ“u fii Alla no Konngol Alla ngol Й“amtora, Й“en goonguЙ“e soodirooЙ“e nguur-aduna fii laakara. Kala on haЙ“idaaЙ—o fii laawol Alla ngol no Й“amtora o sahodini, maa o fooli gaГ±o on, arma Alla Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi ; ko ndin woni Aljanna e Welayee Alla."
  4,75,"E haЙ—i on onon muumini en, waЙ—ugol jihaadi fii Й“amtugol Konngol Alla ngol ? e fii faabagol lo*inaa- Й“e Й“en ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e, e ka fayЙ“e ; Й“en Й“e no toroo Alla Й“e wi'a : ""Joomi amen, Yaltin men Makka tawde yimЙ“e ton Й“en tooГ±irii sirku e jaggitu- gol e jeyaaЙ“e Alla Й“en, WaЙ—anaa Men immorde ka MaaЙ—a on toppitotooЙ—o men, wallitoo men e duГ±u- gol lorra kan""."
  4,76,"GomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en hino haЙ“idee fii Й“amtugol Konngol Alla ngol, heeferЙ“e Й“en hino haЙ“idee fii reweteeЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in. HaЙ“ee weldiiЙ“e seytaane Й“en: pellet, si on haЙ“idii e maЙ“Й“e, ma on foolu Й“e ; tawde pewje seytaane Й—en laatike lo'uЙ—e, Й—e loratah fawiiЙ“e e Alla Й“en."
  4,77,"E a anndaa an NulaaЙ—o, fii yoga e sahaabaaЙ“e maa lamndiiЙ“e yo jihaadi farle e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wi'anaa ado jihaadi ndin farleede : ""Nantee juuЙ—e mon Й—en e jihaadi, Г±iiЙ“non julde, jonnon asakal"", nde Й“e ferunoo Madiina, lislaamu on heЙ“i doole, jihaadi ndin farlaa ; Й—um tedditiri Й“e, Й“e waЙ—ti hulirde yim- Й“e Й“en wano Й“e hulirta non Alla, maa ko Й“uri ngol kulol tiiЙ—ude, Й“e wi'i : ""Joomi amen, ko FarlanЙ—aa hare e dow amen ? Hanno Nennanaa men haa men dakmitora aduna ? Maakan Й“e an NulaaЙ—o: ""Dakamme aduna ko juuti woo lannay, ko laakara Й“uri moЖґЖґannde on hulЙ—o Alla ToowuЙ—o On ; tawde ko ton neema duumotoo, on Й—uytaЕ‹taake golle mon moЖґЖґe yeru hufol tamaroore""."
  4,78,"Kala ka wonЙ—on maayde nden hewtitoto on si lajal ngal timmii, hay si on laatike e kuЙ“eeje mahaaЙ—e ka woЙ—Й—itii nokku hare nden. Si goЙ—Й—um e welo-welo heЙ“ii naafiqi en Й“ee ; wano Й“iЙ—Й—o maa arsike yaajuЙ—o, Й“e wi'ay: ЖЉum Й—oo ko immorde ka Alla"", si saЙ—teende heЙ“iriiЙ“e ka jawdi ma ka Й“iЙ—Й“e ; Й“e kiitinoroo Annabiijo on Й“e wi'a: ""Ndee saЙ—teende ko sabu maa"", maakan Й“ee an NulaaЙ—o : ""MoЖґЖґere nden e bone on fow ko Г‘aawoore Alla e hoddiro Makko"". E ko nanngi Й“ee Й“e Й“attotaako faamude haala-maa?!"
  4,79,"Kala ko heЙ“u maa an Й“iЙ—Й—o Aadama, woni arsikeede Й“iЙ—Й—o maa jawdi ; Й—um ko ЖЃural Alla e dow maaЙ—a, kala kadi ko heЙ“u maa e bone ka jawdi maa ka Й“iЙ—Й“e ; Й—um ko sabu ko woЕ‹kii maa kin faggitii e geddi. GomЙ—ii Men Imminirii ma an Annabiijo, faade e yimЙ“e Й“en, a NulaaЙ—o immorde ka Alla, fii yottingol Nulal Makko ngal. Alla Yonii Seede e goongungol maa ngol ka yottingol."
  4,80,"Kala Й—oftiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on e ko o yamirta kon, o woЙ—Й—itii e ko haЙ—ata kon ; gomЙ—ii haray on Й—on Й—oftike Yamaruyee Alla on. Kala kadi Й—uurniiЙ—o ma an NulaaЙ—o, wata Й—um sunine, tawde Men Nuliraali ma reenoowo golle maЙ“Й“e, ko woni, ko Menen Hasbata ontigi e golle makko Й—en."
  4,81,"Naafiqi en no wi'ane : ""Men Й—oftoto ma"", si Й“e yaltii ka maa, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e suuЙ—itoto fewja ko lunndii kon ko Й“e feГ±Г±inan ma. Alla non no Anndi kon ko Й“e fewjata, O YoЙ“itoyay Й“e nden fewjoore maЙ“Й“e, wata Й—um aanine ; Й“e lorataa ma hay huunde. Hoolor Alla fawoЙ—a e Makko, Alla Yonii HoolorteeЙ—o."
  4,82,"Ko haЙ—ata Й“ee janngugol taskitora Alqur'aana haa fellitana Й“e wonnde lurre alaa e mayre ?! Haa goonga maa kan feeГ±anaЙ“e kadi. Hara nun ndee Qur'aanaare ko nokku goo iwri ko wonaa ka Alla, Й“e tawayno e mare cokko-cakka e lurre heewuЙ—e ka Г±aawooje mayre."
  4,83,"Si fiyaake hoolaare, maa weltaare juulЙ“e Й“en arii e Й“ee naafiqiiЙ“e, walla hara ko kulol juulЙ“e Й“en maa sunaare maЙ“Й“e, Й“e saakitay Й—um. Sinno Й“e ruttuno on fiyaake e NulaaЙ—o on (saw), maa e fewjooЙ“e fii maЙ“Й“e Й“en; Й“en taskotooЙ“e Й“ulnito maЙ“Й“e fotngol gelloreede ko Й“e haani waЙ—de e fii saakitugol maa suuЙ—a fiyaake on. Si wanaano ЖЃural Alla ngal e dow mooЙ—on -onon muumini en- e Yurmeende Makko nde O ЖЉaЙ—ndiri on jarrabuyee naafiqi en ; on jokkayno seytaane si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e mon."
  4,84,"Habu an NulaaЙ—o, fii laawol Alla ngol no Й“amtora, a lamndetaake fii heddiiЙ“e Й“en ; tawde a fawaaka ka hare si wanaa hoore-ma. RerЙ—in gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e hare nden, arma Alla nde DuГ±irta hare mon nden doole heeferЙ“e Й“en. Ko Alla Й“uri TiiЙ—ude doole, ko KaЕ‹ko Й“uri TiiЙ—ude lepte."
  4,85,"Kala on etiiЙ—o e moЖґЖґere o heЙ“ay geЙ“al e mayre, kala kadi on etiiЙ—o e bone o heЙ“ay geЙ“al e makko. Alla Laatike SeeditiiЙ—o e kala kuuЙ—e neЙ—Й—aЕ‹ke Й—en, O YoЙ“itoyay Й“e Й—um, kala e mon wonЙ—a sabu jam o barjee jam, kala wonЙ—a sabu bone heba bone."
  4,86,"Si goЙ—Й—o hiwrike on hiwritee mo ko Й“uri hiwraandu makko ndun, maa rutton sugu hiwraandu makko ndun, ko ruttugol ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude kon Й“urnaa. Pellet, Alla Laatike ReenuЙ—o kala golle mon Й—en, O YoЙ“itoyay kala e golle mun."
  4,87,"Alla, reweteeЙ—o e goonga alaa si wanaa KaЕ‹ko, ma O MooЙ“itoy on fow Г‘alnde Darnga nde sikke alaa e mun ; fii no O YoЙ“itira on golle mon. Alla ЖЃurЙ—o Alla goongude e yeewtere."
  4,88,"Ko waЙ—i on onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en feddeeji Й—iЙ—i e fii Й“ee naafiqiiЙ“e : fedde goo hino wi'a waree Й“e sabu keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e, fedde goo wi'a accireeЙ“e sabu gomЙ—iЙ—al maЙ“Й“e ngal ! On haanaano luutondirde fii maЙ“Й“e. Alla RuttiriiЙ“e e keeferaaku sabu golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. E on faala fewnude on mo Alla Majjini laawol goonga ngol ?! Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a heЙ“aЕ‹taa mo fewnoowo."
  4,89,"Naafiqi en no yeloo sinno on yeddayno kon ko Jippinaa e mooЙ—on wano Й“e yeddiri non, laatoЙ—on fotooЙ“e e ngol yeddugol. Wata on jogito immorde e maЙ“Й“e yiЙ—Й“e haa Й“e fera e laawol Alla ngol immo- immorde galle sirku faade ka leydi lislaamu fii felliЕ‹tingol liimanaaku maЙ“Й“e. Si Й“e Й—uurnike gaay Й—um, nanngee Й“e waron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e. Wata on jogito e maЙ“Й“e giЙ—o, wanaa kadi ko wallindiron e ayЙ“e mooЙ—on."
  4,90,"Si wanaa Й“en Й“e hino jokkoo e maЙ“Й“e faade yimЙ“e Й“e ahodiЙ—on tertagol hare, maaЙ—um Й“e arii on hara Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hino faaЙ—ani haЙ“ugol on, maa haЙ“ugol yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en. Si Alla Haajuno, O Warayno Й“e e mooЙ—on, Й“e haЙ“a on. Wata on haЙ“u Й“e maa dahon. Si Й“e pottitike on, Й“e haЙ“aali on, Й“e arii e mon fii moЖґЖґintingol, haray dey Alla WaЙ—anaali on e dow maЙ“Й“e laawol haЙ“ugol Й“e maa dahugol Й“e."
  4,91,"Onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, arma nde tawoton fedde goo e naafiqi en no feГ±Г±inana on gomЙ—inal fii no Й“e faabinora on, Й“e feГ±Г±inana yimЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en keeferaaku ngun tuma Й“e ruttii e maЙ“Й“e fii no Й“en kadi faabora Й“e. Tuma kala non nde Й“e ruttitaa e yeddugol Alla ngol sirkana Mo, Й“e ugginite e mun ko tiiЙ—i. ЖЃen non si haЙ—itaaki haЙ“ugol on, Й“e ari e mun fii moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol, Й“e haЙ—i juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en meemugol on ; haray nanngee Й“e waron Й“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e. ЖЃen siforiiЙ“e Й—ii sifaaji, Men WaЙ—anii on e nannugol Й“e ngol wara hujja Й“annguЙ—o ; sabu pewje maЙ“Й“e Й“onЙ—e Й—en."
  4,92,"Haananaa gomЙ—inЙ—o nde warata gomЙ—inЙ—o si wanaa hara ko e faljere. Kala warЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o e hoore faljere, hara kaffaara rinЙ—ingol daande gomЙ—inЙ—o waЙ—Й—ike mo, hino fawii yimЙ“e ronooЙ“e warЙ—o on diya (njoЙ“di woЕ‹kii) jonneteeЙ—o ronooЙ“e waraaЙ—o on : si wanaa hara Й“en yaafi on diya. Si waraaЙ—o on ko e yimЙ“e haЙ“ideteeЙ“e mon jeyaa hara ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o, waЙ—Й—oto waruЙ—o on rinЙ—ingol daande gomЙ—inЙ—o, diya fawaaki mo. Si tawii non waraaЙ—o o wanaa gomЙ—inЙ—o, kono non ahadi tertagol hare no hakkunde mon, haray fawoto yimЙ“e ronooЙ“e waruЙ—o on diya jonneteeЙ—o ronooЙ“e waraaЙ—o on, hino fawii waruЙ—o on rinЙ—ingol daande gomЙ—inЙ—o fii kaffaara kuuЙ—e makko Й—en. Si o heЙ“aali ko o rinЙ—ina, maa o roЕ‹kii feere mun, haray ko : yo o hooru lebbi Й—iЙ—i jokkondirЙ—i fii no Alla Tuubirana mo. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o golle jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Sari'a Makko on."
  4,93,"Kala warЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o e hoore tewaare, haray njoЙ“di makko ndin ko naatugol Jahannama, ko o luttoowo e nder magge ; Alla Tikkanii mo, O RaЙ—ike mo e Yurmeende Makko, O Hebilanii mo lepte mawЙ—e sabu faggitagol mo Й—ii junuubi mawЙ—i."
  4,94,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, si on fokitanii jihaadi, tabitinee fii Й“en Й“e haЙ“idoton, wata on wi'an on feГ±Г±inanЙ—o on lislaamu mu'un : ""Wanaa a gomЙ—inЙ—o, ko hulangol jawdi maa ndin e woЕ‹kii maa kin fawu maa Й—um"", waron mo fii Й—aЙ“Й“ere konhoyri ; dakamme aduna, ko ka Alla non konhoyri Й—uuЙ—undi woni ; ko ndin kadi Й“uri moЖґЖґude e konhoyri. Ko wano on suuЙ—uЙ—o gomЙ—inal mun e yimЙ“e mun Й“en wa'unoЙ—on ko adii, Alla MoЖґЖґorii e mon lislaamu on O ЖЉaЙ—ndi ЖґiiЖґe mon. Taskee. Pellet, huunde e golle mon Й—en suuЙ—aaki Alla, O YoЙ“itoyay on e Й—um."
  4,95,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e roЕ‹kuЙ“e yahude jihaadi fii laawol Alla ngol, hara wanaa joomiraaЙ“e ngaЕ‹to Й“en hono nawnuЙ“e, maa wumЙ“e), fotataa e Й“en tiiЙ—norЙ“e ka jihaadi ton jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en e woЕ‹kiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in. Alla ЖЃurnirii tiiЙ—noriiЙ“e jawle mun Й—en e woЕ‹kiiji mun Й—in, dow Й“en roЕ‹kuЙ“e yahude jihaadi, darja. Kala maЙ“Й“e hino fodaa moЖґЖґere ko o hanndi kon, Alla non ЖЃurnirii tiiЙ—niiЙ“e Й“en e dow jooЙ—iiЙ“e Й“en, mbarjaari mawndi."
  4,96,"ЖЉum ko darjaaji fawondirayЙ—i, wonndude e haforaneede junuubi, e Yurmegol Й“e. Alla Laatike Haforanoowo jeyaaЙ“e Mun Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  4,97,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e Malaa'ika warata , hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e tooГ±irЙ“e pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in salagol ferude yaha e leydi lislaamu, Malaa'ika en hino fela Й“e wi'a tuma woЕ‹kiiji maЙ“Й“e yaltata : ""Ko e honЙ—um wonunoЙ—on e mun ?!, ko senndi on e sirkooЙ“e Й“en ?!"" ЖЃe jaabi- tora ngaЕ‹tinagol wi'a :""Men laatinoke lo'inaaЙ“e Й“e alaa fiira e feere"". Malaa'ika en wi'ana Й“e : ""Hari leydi Alla ndin yaajaa haa ka roЕ‹kon yaltude fii no daЙ—idiron e diina mon koyraa ?! ЖЃen Й—on roЕ‹ku Й“e feraana, werde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde e Г±iiЙ“irde."
  4,98,"Hino ittintinaa e on kammbaa, Й“en lo'inaaЙ“e jogitiiЙ“e nganto ka worЙ“e, e ka rewЙ“e e ka fayЙ“e ; Й“en Й“e alaa doole pottingol tooГ±e Й—en e maЙ“Й“e maa hara Й“e alaa feere Й“oortagol Й—en tooГ±e. ЖЃen Й—on, arma Alla nde yawtirana Й“e yurmeende Makko, Alla Laatike yawtanoowo jeyaaЙ“e Makko tuubooЙ“e Й“en."
  4,99,"4:98"
  4,100,"Kala on feruЙ—o iwi e leydi keeferaaku faade e leydi lislaamu fii Й—aЙ“Й“ugol Welayee Alla, o heЙ“oyay e leydi ndi o feri e mun ndin waylorde e leydi ndi wonah ndi o acci ndi, o danay ko Й“uri leydi ndi o o heЙ“ay ton teddungal, e arsike yaajuЙ—o. Kala kadi yaltuЙ—o e suudu mu'un ko o feruЙ—o faade e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, hooti maayde nden hewtitii mo ado o hewtoyde ka ferirde makko, gomЙ—ii mbarjaari makko ndin tabitii ka Alla. Alla Laatike hafranoowo tuubuЙ—o e jayaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  4,101,"Si on Й—atniima , ka leydi on ngalah bakkaat e ustude juulde nde darЙ—e nay njuulon nde darЙ—e Й—iЙ—e, tawde on kuli nde huunde aГ±aande yana- ta e mon ummorde e heefereeЙ“em, heefereeЙ“e ina ngaГ±i mon gaГ±gol Й“anngungol, tabiti e sunna dagaade ustde juulde e Й—atngal e saanga hoolaare."
  4,102,"Si a tawdaama e maЙ“Й“e ka konu hare, an NulaaЙ—o, a faandike juulnugol Й“e, senndu konu ngu pecce Й—iЙ—i : feccere goo juulida e maaЙ—a Й“e jogitoo jogaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka julde, ndeya feccere ayna Й“e, si feccere aranere nden juulidii e imaamu on darnde, yo Й“e timminan hoore-maЙ“Й“e julde nden, si Й“e juulii, yo Й“e darto Й“aawo mooЙ—on Й“e fewta ayЙ“e Й“en, ndeya feccere Й—iЙ—aЙ“ere reenaynoode nde juulaali kadi ara, Й“e juulida e imaamu on darnde, si imaamu on salminii, Й“e timmiЕ‹tinoo julde maЙ“Й“e nden Й“e jogitoroo jogaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in fii ayЙ“e Й“en. HeeferЙ“e Й“en yelinoke sinno on welsindotono e Й—ii jogaaji mon e doЕ‹le mon tuma juuloton, Й“e yana e mooЙ—on yanannde wootere, Й“e juha on e welsindaare mon. Bakkaatu fawaaki on si tawii lorra toЙ“o maa nawnaare heЙ“ii on ekn, nde walliЕ‹ton jogaaji mon Й—in, ko woni tun, reЕ‹toree e ayЙ“e mon Й“en no newori woo. Pellet, Alla Hebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoynooje."
  4,103,"Si on timminii julde nden, onon gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, jaЕ‹toree Innde Alla nden subbunhinagol, e hamdinagol e haylilugol foti on dari, maa hara on juuЙ—i maa ko e hoore becce mon. Si kulol ngol iwii e mo'on on deeЖґii, haray Г±iЙ“nee julde nden no timmiri wonndude e waЙ—Й—iiЙ—i mayre. Pellet, julde nden laatike ko farlaande e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en waqiЕ‹tinaande ; dagotaako neЙ“nirgol nde si wanaa gaЕ‹to, si tawii non ko e Й—anngal, haray hiwo dagoo hawtitugol renndinde e ustude."
  4,104,"Wata on lo'iЕ‹kino onon muumini en, maajaasikino- Й—on e nder Й—aЙ“Й“itugol heeferЙ“e ayЙ“e mon Й“en. Si on laatike hiЙ—on muusee e ko heЙ“ata on e barme maa wareede, kamЙ“e kadi hiЙ“e muusiree wano muusirteЙ—on, wata Й“e Й“uru on muГ±Г±aare ; sabu onon hiЙ—on jortii immorde e Alla mbarjaari e ballal kon ko Й“e jortaaki. Pellet, Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o fiyakuuji jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Makko ngol Sari'aaji Makko Й—in."
  4,105,"Menen men Jippinii e maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, ndee Qur'aanaare wonndude e goonga fii yo a Г±aawir hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kala fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e kon ko Alla Hollu maa. Wata a wonan janfotooЙ“e Й“en wennjanoowo Й“e."
  4,106,"ЖЉaЙ“Й“ir Alla yaafuyee e haforaneede. Pellet, Alla Laatike Haforanoowo kala tuubanЙ—o Mo e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  4,107,"Wota a wennjondire fii on neЙ—Й—o fantinoowo janfa, suuЙ—a janfa mun. Pellet, Alla YiЙ—aa Й“en fenooЙ“e heewЙ“e janfa e bakkaat."
  4,108,"HiЙ“e suuЙ—oo yimЙ“e Й“en hersa maa kulol tuma Й“e yeddata kono Й“e suuЙ—otaako Alla, KaЕ‹ko le Himo Wonndi e maЙ“Й“e HuuЙ“iti Й“e tuma Й“e fewjata kon ko O Welaaka e konngol; wano hiwawande bakkondinЙ—o e tooГ±ugol mo wi'aa-waЙ—aa. Alla Laatike HuЙ“indiiЙ—o kon ko Й“e gollata kene e gunndoo, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um, O YoЙ“itoyay Й“e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  4,109,"Hey mon yo Й“e'e himmirЙ“e fiyaake Й“en faggatooЙ“e bone, on wennjii fii maЙ“Й“e ka nguurda aduna fii laЙ“Й“inngol Й“e, daЙ—naЙ“e Г±aaweede. E ko hommbo non wennjanoyta Й“e Alla Г‘alnde Darngal tuma fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e anndaa fii mun, kaa ko hommbo laatantooЙ“e fawtiiЙ—o nden Г‘alnde ?! Sikke alaa wonnde gooto hattanaaka Й—um."
  4,110,"Kala golluЙ—o ko boni maa o tooГ±iri hoore makko geddi, hooti o Й—aЙ“Й“iri Alla haforaneede, o qirritii bone on, o nimsi, o taway Alla ko Haforoowo bone makko on, HinnotooЙ—o mo poomaa."
  4,111,"Kala faggitiiЙ—o bone ; Й—uuЙ—i famЙ—i, pellet, lepte mun Й—en ko e makko tun yanata. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o golle jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Sari'a Makko on."
  4,112,"Kala kadi faggitorЙ—o faljere goopol maa bakkadin-tewaare hooti o tooГ±iri Й—um goЙ—Й—o goo daЙ—ndiiЙ—o e on bone, gomЙ—ii haray o ronnditike fenaande tiiЙ—unde e bakkaatu Й“annguЙ—o."
  4,113,"Si wanaano ЖЃural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, pellet, fedde goo e Й“ee janfatooЙ“e ko'e mum en himmirayno majjingol ma gaay e goonga kan roЕ‹kaa Г±aawirde nunЙ—al. Tgi rigi on, Й“e alaa e majjinnde si wanaa pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in ; sabu lepte golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko e maЙ“Й“e yiltotoo. Alla Jippinii Qur'aana e sunna haa e maaЙ—a, O Anndinii ma peewal O Ndayginan maa ko a anndaano. ЖЃural Alla ngal e dow maaЙ—a (Annabaaku ngun e ndeenka) laatike mawnu-Й—um."
  4,114,"MoЖґЖґere alaa e ko heewi e haala maЙ“Й“e kaЙ“e gun- ndata hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, si wanaa kan haala yamirayka ittugol sadaka, maa moЖґЖґere nde diina kan tinndini e mun maa moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol hakkunde pooЙ—ondirЙ“e. Kala huuwirЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla on, arma Men Okka mo baraaji mawndi."
  4,115,"Kala lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on e kon ko o addi Й“aawo nde peewal ngal feeГ±annde mo, o jokki laawol goo ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men Acciday mo e ko o suЙ“ii kon o majjira sawaaba on sabu Й—uurnagol goonga kan, Men Naadoya mo yiite Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde !"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla YawtaЕ‹taa kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, O Naaday sirkoowo on yiite, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um e geddi wonannde on Mo O Muuyiri ЖЃural e Yurmeende Makko. Kala o kafiduЙ—o e Alla goЙ—Й—o goo, gomЙ—ii on Й—on ooГ±orike e goonga kan ooГ±annde woЙ—Й—iinde ; tawde o fotnii TaguЙ—o On e tagaaЙ—o on."
  4,117,"KO ЖЃen sirkooЙ“e rewata, Й“e rewida Й—um e Alla, si wanaa sanamuuji rewЙ—iniraaЙ—i inЙ—e rewЙ“e ; wano Laata, e 'Uzzaa, Й—i lorrataa Й—i nafataa. ЖЃe alaa e rewude ka haqiiqa, si wanaa seytaniiru yaltundu e Й—oftaare Alla ; tawde ko ndun yamiri Й“e rewugol sanamu."
  4,118,"Ko Й—um si Alla WoЙ—Й—iniri ndu e Yurmeende Makko nden, ndun seytaaniiru huЙ—anii Joomi mayru ndu wi'i: ""Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaЙ“e Maa Й“en geЙ“al anndangal, ngal mi majjinoyta e goonga kan."
  4,119,"Ma mi faloЙ“e gaay e laawol focciingol ngol, ma mi yelinyЙ“e yela fenaande ko no cuЙ—inana Й“e majjere nden, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e taygol noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in fii harmingol ko Alla Dagini kon e majji, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e waylugol tagu Alla ngun"". Kala on jogitorЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o, gomЙ—ii haray on Й—on sooyii sooyannde Й“anngunde."
  4,120,"Seytaande no foda Й“e penaale, himo yelina Й“e mehre, o alaa e yelinnde Й“e si wanaa mehre."
  4,121,"ЖЃen jokkuЙ“e Й—ate seytaane Й—en e kon ko mbo fida- taЙ“e, Г±iiЙ“irde maЙ“Й“e nden ko ka yiite Jahannama, Й“e heЙ“ataa gaay e magge moolorde."
  4,122,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe, aray nde Men Naada Й“e Aljannaaji Й—i ila senngo ley kuЙ“eeje majji canЙ—i : ko Й“e duumiЕ‹teeЙ“e nder ton poomaa. ЖЉum ko fodoore immorde ka Alla. Fodoore Alla nden non ko nde goongaare, O Lunndotaako fodoore. Alaa Й“urЙ—o Alla goongude e konngol."
  4,123,"DaЙ—ugol ngol laatoraaki sabu yelaaji mon Й—in onon juulЙ“e Й“en maa sabu yelaaji yimЙ“e Defte Й“en. Si ko woni, Й—um ko golle Й—en jokki. Kala on golluЙ—o e mooЙ—on golle bonЙ—e o yoЙ“ete Й—um Г‘alnde Darngal, o heЙ“anoytaake ko woori Alla giЙ—o Й“aЙ—noowo nafa wanaa ballo duГ±anoowo lorra."
  4,124,"Kala on golluЙ—o immorde e golle moЖґЖґe, foti ko gorko maaЙ—um debbo, hara kaЕ‹ko ko o gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla ToowuЙ—o On, Й“en Й—on moftuЙ“e gomЙ—inal e golle, Й“e naatoyay Aljanna, Й“e Й—uytanoytaake e moЖґЖґi maЙ“Й“e Й—in ko fotata e gurun tamaro."
  4,125,"Alla Й“urЙ—o moЖґЖґude diina haa hewta on jebbilaniiЙ—o Alla kene e gunndoo o laЙ“Й“ini anuyee makko, o moЖґЖґini golle makko Й—en, o jokki diina Annabi Ibraahiima kan, iwdi diina Muhammadu (yo o his), ooГ±iiЙ—o gaay e sirku e keeferaaku faade e tawhiidi e gomЙ—inal. Alla SuЙ“ike Ibraahiima Annabiijo Makko (yo o his), O YiЙ—iri mo giggol timmungol e nder tagu Makko ngun denndaangal."
  4,126,"Ko Alla Tan Woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Alla Laatike HuЙ“indoriiЙ—o Anndal e Kattal e Toppitagol kala huunde e tagu Makko ngun."
  4,127,"HiЙ“e lamndo maa an NulaaЙ—o, fii rewЙ“e Й“en e ko waЙ—Й—ii fee maЙ“Й“e e dow maЙ“Й“e, maaku: ""Alla no ЖЃannginannde on lamndal mon ngal, O ЖЃanngina- na on kon ko janngetee e dow mooЙ—on ka Quraana fii Й“en alyatiimaaЙ“e rewЙ“e Й“e tammbitiЙ—on, Й“en Й“e on jonnataa kon ko Alla Farlani Й“e immorde e teЕ‹e e ndonndi, on rerЙ—ataa fii resugol Й“e hiЙ—on salora kadi goЙ—Й—o goo resira Й“e miilegol jawle maЙ“e, himo ЖЃannginana on kadi kon ko waЙ—Й—ii on e Й“en lo'iaaЙ“e jolta duuЙ“i'en fii no jonnitiron Й“e haqqee maЙ“Й“e on ka ndonndi, O HaЙ—a on Г±aamugol jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, himo ЖЃannginana on kadi wonnde no waЙ—Й—ii on daranagol alyatiimaaЙ“e Й“en nunЙ—al. Kala ko huuwuЙ—on e moЖґЖґere fii alyatiima en e woЙ—Й“e goo, pellet, Alla no Anndi Й—um, O YoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  4,128,"Si debbo hulirii moodi mun Й“urnitaare e Й—uurnaare, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o bakkaat nde Й“e moЖґЖґiЕ‹tinira sulhu debbo on jippitotoo e haqqeeji makko goo wano nafaqqa maa mbalndi. Ko sulhu on Й“uri moЖґЖґannde Й“e cergal ngal, pittaali Й—in anndiraama nguddam, Й—i heewaa jippitaade e haqqee majji, haani ka resindirЙ“e Й“en Г±awndata ngun Г±awu Й—on e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e elta pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in e muГ±Г±ondiral e moЖґЖґinngol. Si on moЖґЖґinii on hulii Alla ; on Й—oftike Yamruyeeji Makko Й—in o woЙ—Й—itike HaЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in, pellet, Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton, huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo, O YoЙ“itoyay on Й—um."
  4,129,"Onon worЙ“e Й“en on waawataa nunЙ—irde mbaadi timmundi hakkunde rewЙ“e mon Й“en, hay si on rerЙ—ii e Й—um ; Й—um ko sabu on maraa feere-mun, wata tun on ooГ±o kala ooГ±annde e on mo on yiЙ—aa, tertoron mo wa yowaaЙ—o mo alaa moodi ko toppitoo mo. Si on moЖґЖґinii hakkunde mon on muГ±Г±ondirii hakkunde resindirЙ“e, on hulii Alla, pellet, Alla Laatike Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o on."
  4,130,"Si resandirЙ“e ceertarii ceergal wollo Й“oorgu Alla yondina gooto e mum en fof e Й“ural Makko jaacngal Alla seeraani wonde ko jaacЙ—o Й“ural e yurmeende jom Г±eeГ±al e yiilde fiyakuuji e hoddirde."
  4,131,"Ko Alla Tun Woodani denndaangal ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi e laamagol ko woni hakkunde majji. GomЙ—ii Men Ahodii e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, Men Ahodi kadi e mooЙ—on, wonnde : ""Hulee Alla, Й—oftoЙ—on Yamirooje Makko reЕ‹toЙ—on e HaЙ—aaЙ—i Makko !"". Si on firtii ahadi ndin, haray on lorree hoore-mon, Alla kan ko Galo YonndinorЙ—o dewe mon, ko KaЕ‹ko Jey kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, ko O YonndiniiЙ—o e kala tagu Makko ngun, ko O YettiniiЙ—o e kala Sifaaji Makko e KuuЙ—e Makko."
  4,132,"Ko Alla Tun Heeranii jeygol kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, HannduЙ—o Й—ofteede. Alla Yonii FawtotooЙ—o Toppitoo kala fiyaake tagu Makko ngun."
  4,133,"Si Mo YiЙ—i, O Lannay fii mon, onon yo yimЙ“e, O Adda woЙ—Й“e goo ko Й—oftotooЙ“e Mo Й“e yeddataa Mo. Alla Laatike HattanЙ—o Й—um."
  4,134,"Kala e mon tawЙ—o ko mbarjaari aduna ndin tun faalaa, yo o anndu Alla No Jogii mbarjaari aduna e laakara, yo o Й—aЙ“Й“u Й—in Й—iЙ—i immorde ka Makko. Alla Laatike Naatike Nanoowo jeewte mon, ReenuЙ—o golle mon, O YoЙ“itoyay on e Й—um."
  4,135,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o, Г±iiЙ“ee e nunЙ—al, seedoЙ—on goonga, hay si tawii non ko e hoore-mon, maa e hoore jibimЙ“e on Й“en maa Й“adondiraaЙ“e mon Й“en. Wata ngalu maa baasal goЙ—Й—o sakko on e seedagol ngol, tawde ko Alla ЖЃuri Hanndude on baaso maaЙ—um galo. Wata on jokku mbeleeЙ—e Й—en ka seedagol haa ooГ±oЙ—on gaay e goonga kan. Si on waylii seedagol ngol on seedorike noone goo, maa on Й—uurnike e seedagol ngol ; haray pellet, Alla Laatike HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon."
  4,136,"Ko ono yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla, holle hiЙ—on gomЙ—ini Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e Qur'aanaare Jippiinde nden e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, e Defte JippinaaЙ—e Й—en e Й“eya NulaaЙ—o adinooЙ“e mo. Kala yedduЙ—o Alla, e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e Defte Makko Й—en, e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en e Г‘alande Darngal ; gomЙ—ii haray o woЙ—Й—ondirii e laawol focciingol ngol."
  4,137,"Pellet, Й“en yiltitotooЙ“e tuma kala e keeferaaku Й“aawo nde Й“e gomЙ—innoo, refti Й“e maayde e ngun keeferaaku ; Alla Laatoraali Yawtanoowo Й“e junuubi wanaa kadi O Fewnoowo Й“e e laawol focciingol."
  4,138,"An NulaaЙ—o, welinir naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en, wonnde no woodani Й“e immorde ka Alla, lepte muusuЙ—e Г‘alnde Darngal."
  4,139,"ЖЉen lepte maЙ“Й“e, ko tawde Й“e jogitike heeferЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—Й“e wallondirteeЙ“e ko wanaa gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Й—um maЙ“Й“e no haawnii ! E Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“iray Й“e cemmbe e doole ko Й“e Й“amtora ?! Pellet, cemmbe e doole fow ko Alla Heeranii."
  4,140,"GomЙ—ii Alla Jippinii e mooЙ—on onon muumini en, e ndee Qur'aanaare Teddunde wonnde : ""Si on nanii Aayeeje Alla Й—en no yeddee jalkitee e jonnde, haray ko yo on immo Й—on haa nde Й“en Й—on fuЙ—Й—itoyii yewtere goo nde wanaa yeddugol jalkita Aayeeje Alla Й—en, si on jooЙ—odii non e maЙ“Й“e fewndo ka yeddta jalkita Й—on Aayeeje Й—en, haray on nanndii e maЙ“Й“e e lunndagol Yamiroore Alla nden ; tawde on jaЙ“aali immagol e jonnde maЙ“Й“e nden. Pellet, Alla ko MooЙ“oyoowo naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en e heeferЙ“e Й“en fow ka yiite Jahannama Г‘alnde Darngal."
  4,141,"ЖЃen habbittooЙ“e on bone maa moЖґЖґere, si on daГ±ii polgal on heЙ“ii konuheyri, Й“e wi'ana on : ""E men wonndaano e mo'on, men tawdaa ko tawdaa ko tawdaЙ—on ?! Fii no Й“e heЙ“ira geЙ“al, si heeferЙ“e Й“en heЙ“ii geЙ“al, Й“e wi'ana Й“e : ""E men toppitanooki on, men etii no fooliron men reeni on gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ?! Alla Ko Г‘aawoyoowo hakkunde mo'on fow Г‘alnde Darngal ; O Naada gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Aljanna, O Naada naafiqii Й“e Й“en ka ndenka Й“urka joltude ka nder yiite, Alla WaЙ—irantaa Heefer- Й“e Й“en ЖЃural Makko ngal hujja e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Г‘alnde Darngal, si ko woni, O WaЙ—anay gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en battane moЖґЖґe."
  4,142,"Pellet, naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en hino janforo Alla hollirde islaam e suuЙ—de keefeeru, Kanko kadi O YoЙ“itiray Й“e janfa maЙ“Й“e sabu O reeni ЖґiiЖґe mum en wondude ko O anndi ko keefeeru mum en, O heblana Й“e lepte sattuЙ—e ka Laakara.Si Й“e immanike julde nden, Й“e immoray ngaameelo, Й“e jantotaako wondude e aГ±de juulde nde woni faandaare mum en tan ko yeengo e mawnineede, Й“e cellintah ngam Alla, Й“e njantataaka Alla si wonah setta si Й“e haynii gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en."
  4,143,"ЖЃen naafiqiiЙ“e no denngi-denndinan e weemre hakkunde Й—on, Й“e wonndaa e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en Й“e wonndaa e heeferЙ“e Й“en. Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a heЙ“antaa mo an NulaaЙ—o, laawol no o feewira."
  4,144,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, wata on jogitor heeferЙ“e Й“en weldiiЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e e hoore gomЙ—imЙ“e. E on faalira ngal kuugal mon nde waЙ—anton Alla e dow mooЙ—on hujja Й“annguЙ—o mo hanndirayЙ—on lepte ?!"
  4,145,"Pellet, Alla WaЙ—oyay naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en ka Й“uri joltude Й—on e ndenka yiite Г‘alnde Darngal, a heЙ“antaa Й“e non ballo duГ±anoowo Й“e Й—en lepte !"
  4,146,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e ruttii e Alla iwde e naafige, Й“e moЖґЖґini golle maЙ“Й“e, Й“e jogitii ahadi Alla ndin Й“e laЙ“Й“inani Alla golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en. ЖЃen siforoЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, Й“e wonndii e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en aduan e laakara. Arma Alla YeЙ—a gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,147,"Alla Haajaaka e leptugol on si on jaarnii Mo on gomЙ—inii Mo, si O Leptiray on ko junuubi mon Й—in. Si on moЖґЖґinii golle, on yettii Mo on gomЙ—inii Mo kene e gunndoo, alaa ko O Leptira on. Alla Laatike Jaarnoowo kala yettuЙ—o Neemaaji Makko Й—in, AnnduЙ—o gomЙ—inal tagu Makko ngun, O YoЙ“itoyay kala e golle mun Й—en."
  4,148,"Alla yiЙ—aa feГ±Г±inirgol bone on konngol, Himo AГ±i Й—um Kammbani Й—um, kono on tooГ±aaЙ—o, hino daganoo mo feГ±Г±inirgol bone on konngol fii wullita- gol ko o tooГ±aa kon o yottoo, ko si o muГ±Г±ike non Й“uri moЖґЖґude. Alla Laatike Nanoowo konnguЙ—i mon, AnnduЙ—o Annuyeeji mon, reЕ‹tee e wowlugol ko boni maa faandorgol Й—um."
  4,149,"Si on feГ±Г±inirii konngol maa kuugal kala moЖґЖґere, maa on suuЙ—ii nde maa on yaafanike on bonnuЙ—o e mo'on ; pellet, Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o HattanЙ—o, yo yaafagol ngol wonu jikku mon, belajo'o, Alla Yawtanay on."
  4,150,"Pellet, Й“en wonuЙ“e yeddude Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, hiЙ“e faalaa nde Й“e senndata hakkunde Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en ; nde Й“e gomЙ—iЕ‹ta Mo Й“e yedda NulaaЙ“e Й“en, hiЙ“e wi'a : ""MeЙ—en gomЙ—ina yoga e NulaaЙ“e Й“en men yedda yoga maЙ“Й“e"", hiЙ“e faalaa nde Й“e jogitorta hakkunde ngol yeddugol maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—ina Й—on, laawol daЙ—ndatngol Й“e."
  4,151,"ЖЃen Й—on jokkuЙ“e ngol laawol, ko kamЙ“e woni heeferЙ“e Й“en tigiri ; tawde mo yeddii NulaaЙ“e Й“en maa yoga emaЙ“Й“e, haray o yeddii Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en. Men Hebilanii heeferЙ“e Й“en lepte hoy- nooje Г‘alnde Darngal ; Й—um le ko fii Й“e townitanike gomЙ—ingol Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en."
  4,152,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e bajjinЙ—ini Mo, Й“e kafidaali goЙ—Й—o goo, Й“e goongini NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en den- ndaangal, Й“e senndaali hakkunde gooto e maЙ“Й“e wano heeferЙ“e Й“en gerdiri ; Й“en Й—on, arma Alla Okka Й“e njoЙ“di Mawndi e ngal gomЙ—inal maЙ“Й“e e golle maЙ“Й“e moЖґЖґe. Alla Laatike YaafotooЙ—o kala tuubuЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, HinnotooЙ—o Й“e."
  4,153,"Alyahuuda no lamndo maa an NulaaЙ—o, nde jippin- taa e dow maЙ“Й“e Deftere immorde ka kammu won Й“e lamndornoo Muusaa. ЖЉum ko maande e goon-ngugol maaЙ—a, wata a mawnin fii Й—um e maЙ“Й“e, gomЙ—ii adinooЙ“e Й“e lamndinoke Muusaa ko Й“uri Й—um mawnude ; Й“e lamndino mo nde o hollata Й“e Alla e kene pettan. Lepte Й—en faЙ—Й—ini Й“e, hooti Alla Wuurni Й“e, Й“e rewi ngaari ndin ko woori Alla Й“aawo nde Aayeeje ЖЃannguЙ—e Й—en ari e maЙ“Й“e tinndingol gootaagu Alla ngun. Hooti Men Yawtani Й“e Men Okki Muusaa hujja Й“annguЙ—o e yimЙ“e makko Й“en."
  4,154,"Men ЖЃamtiri senngo dow maЙ“Й“e fello ngon sabu ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin no Й“e hunnira ndin, Men Wi'ani Й“e Й“aawo Й—um : ""Naatiree Bayt al Maqdisi on ko on naayiiЙ“e"", Й“e hucci Й“e naati, Men Wi'ani Й“e : ""Wata on jaggitir Г±alnde asewe nden yunngugol"", haЙ—aali Й“e jaggiti Й“e yunngi, Men Nanngi e maЙ“Й“e ahadi tiiЙ—undi, Й“e firti ahadi ndin."
  4,155,"Men RaЙ—ori Й“e e Yurmeende Amen nden sabu ko Й“e firti kon ahadi maЙ“Й“e ndin, e ko Й“e yeddi kon Aayeeje Alla Й—en, e ko Й“e suusi kon warude AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en e ko Й“e wi'ani ko Muhammadu (yo o his) : ""ЖЃerЙ—e amen Й—en ko sokiiЙ—e, Й—e fahmataa ko wowlataa"", tawi non Й“e fenay, si ko woni, Alla Notii e Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й—e nafitortaa moЖґЖґere Й“e gomЙ—intaa si wanaa seeЙ—a, Й—um le nafataa Й“e."
  4,156,"Men HuЙ—iri Й“e kadi sabu keeferaaku maЙ“Й“e ngun, e ko Й“e tukkiri kon Maryama (yo o his) jeeno fenannde mawnde."
  4,157,"Men HuЙ—iri Й“e mantorgol Й“e fenaande wi'a : Menen men warii Almasiihu on, Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama, NulaaЙ—o Alla on"". ЖЃe warano mo non, men fempaano mo wano Й“e nodditorta Й—um, si ko woni, ko gorko mo Alla Nanndini e Iisaa Й“e wari Й“e fempi, Й“e sikki Й“e warii Iisaa. ЖЃen nodditii Й“e warugol Iisaa ka AlyahuudaaЙ“e e Й“en AnnasaaraaЙ“e jonnituЙ“e Iisaa Alyahuuda en, Й“e fow Й“e wonii sikkitaare fii makko, Й“e alaa anndal e fii makko, ko sikke tun Й“e jokki, sikke Й—en non duncataa hay huunde e goo-nga kan. ЖЃe waraali Iisaa, Й“e fempaali mo pellet."
  4,158,"Si ko woni, Alla DaЙ—nduno mo bone maЙ“Й“e on, O ЖЃatiri mo faade ka Makko. Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o e Laamateeri Mun, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Toppitagol Mun Г‘aa- wooje e Sari'aaji Makko."
  4,159,"Alaa hay e gooto e yimЙ“e Defte Й“en, si wanaa o gomЙ—onay Iisaa (yo o his) tuma o jippoytoo ado maayde makko nden ka jamaanu sakkitoru. Г‘alnde Darngal non, Iisaa wonoyay seeditotooЙ—o e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en ; hakkunde ko hawri e ko lunndii sari'a on."
  4,160,"Ko sabu tooГ±e Alyahuuda Й—en, Men toЕ‹irani Й“e yoga e Г±aameteeji laaЙ“uЙ—i daganinooЙ—i Й“e, Men Harminani Й“e kala jom feЙ—aandu, Men Harminani Й“e ka na'i e ka dammi ; Й“ellere majji on si wanaa kon ko roondii Й—um Й“abbe majji on, kadi ko sabu sakkagol Й“e ko'e maЙ“Й“e sakkoo woЙ—Й“e goo e laawol Alla ngol haa Й—um woni jikku maЙ“Й“e."
  4,161,"E sabu gollugol Й“e e ribaa on Й“aawo nde Alla HaЙ—i Й“e e Й—um, e sabu Г±aamugol Й“e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en ko aldaa e goonga. Men Hebilanii yedduЙ“e Й“en e maЙ“Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e."
  4,162,"Kono Й“en AlyahuudaaЙ“e tutiiЙ“e e ganndal, e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, hiЙ“e goongina nden Al Qur'aanaare nden Alla Jippini e maaЙ—a, an NulaaЙ—o, e Й—en Defte JippinaaЙ—e e NulaaЙ“e adinooЙ“e ma ; wano Tawreeta e Linjiila, hiЙ“e Г±iiЙ“na julde nden, Й“e totta zakka on, Й“e goongina wonnde Alla ko Bajjo Mo kafidetaake, Й“e goongina fii Darngal ; Й“en Й—on, arma Men Okka Й“e njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,163,"Menen Men Wahyinii e maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, wano Men Wahyinirnoo e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en ado maaЙ—a, wanaa e maa Й—um fuЙ—Й—ori. Men Wahyiri- no faade Nuuhu, Men Wahyini kadi faade e Й“en AnnabaaЙ“e arnooЙ“e caggal Makko, Men Wahyini faade e Ibraahiima, e Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“en Й—iЙ—o : Ismaa'iila e Ishaaqa, e faade e Yaaquuba Й“iЙ—Й—o Ishaaqa, e Asbaati'en (Й“en woni jeyanooЙ“e e leЖґЖґi banii-israa'iila'en Й—in sappo e Й—iЙ—i ka Й“iЙ—Й“e Yaaquuba jom-kisiee). Men Okki Daawuuda Deftere Jabuura nden."
  4,164,"NulaaЙ“e Amen goo, Men Qissanike ma fii maЙ“Й“e ka Qu'raana, woЙ—Й“e goo, Men Qissanaaki ma fii maЙ“Й“e ; Men Acciri Й—um hikma. Alla Yewtidii e Muusaa ka Annabaaku -ko aldaa e heedo- yewtere haqiiqa hawrannde SeniiЙ—o On, teddungal wonan- nde Muusa."
  4,165,"Men NuliriiЙ“e wewlinirgol mbarjaari teddundi immorde ka Alla, e jertingol yeddooЙ“e Й“en hulЙ“inira Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e fii wata hujja laatano yimЙ“e Й“en e hoore Alla Й“aawo nde O Nuli NulaaЙ“e Й“en. Alla Laatike FooluЙ—o e Laamu Makko, Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o e Г‘aawoore Makko."
  4,166,"Si Alyahuuda'en yeddii ma, pellet, Alla Kan no Goongini kon ko O Jippini e maaЙ—a immorde e Al Qur'aana, an NulaaЙ—o. O JippiniI e mayre Anndal Makko ngal O Faandii ЖіelliЕ‹tinnde JeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, e kon ko O YiЙ—i O Yarlii, maa O kon ko O AГ±i O Salii. Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en no seeditoo wonndude e Seedee Alla On goongude kon ko addu-Й—aa. Alla non Yonii Seedee."
  4,167,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Annabaaku maaЙ—a, Й“e palii yimЙ“e Й“en gaay e lislaamu on, gomЙ—ii Й“e majjirii goonga kan majjere woЙ—Й—ude."
  4,168,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, Й“e tooГ±iri pittaali maЙ“Й“e Й—in heddagol e keeferaaku, Alla Wonaali Yawtanoowo Й“e faale maЙ“Й“e hedda- gol e keeferaaku, wanaa nde O Fewnata Й“e faade e laawol daЙ—irngol lepte Makko Й—en."
  4,169,"Si wanaa ngol laawol naadayngol Jahannama, ko Й“e luttinteeЙ“e ton poomaa. ЖЉum Й—on laatike newanii Й—um Alla, hay huunde O Ronkataa."
  4,170,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! GomЙ—ii NulaaЙ—o Muhammadu (jom-kisiyee) addanii on peewal e diina goonga immorde ka Alla ToowuЙ—o On, gomЙ—inee kon ko o addani on heЙ“on moЖґЖґere aduna e laakara. Si on yeddii Alla, anndde pellet, Ko O YonndiniiЙ—o e gomЙ—inal mon, keeferaaku mon lorrataa Mo, Ko Kanko Woodani laamu kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi e ko woni hakkunde majji. Alla Laatike Anndu on hannduЙ—o e peewal O Newinana mo ngal, O Majjina on mo haanduЙ—o e maggal, Г‘eeГ±u- Й—o e Daalol Makko e Golle Makko e Sari'a Makko e Kattal Makko."
  4,171,"Maaku an NulaaЙ—o, wi'anaa Annasaara'en yimЙ“e Linjiila : ""Wata on fantin ka diina mon, wata on wowlu e hoore Alla fii Annabi Iisaa si wanaa goonaga kan. Pellet, Mema-sella Iisaa Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on, ko NulaaЙ—o Alla mo O Nuliri goonga, O Tagirii mo Daalol Makko ngol O Nuliri Jibriilu (yo o his) faade e Maryam, ngol woni : Laato, O Laatii. ЖЉum ko wuttaandu ndu Alla Nuliri Jibriilu yo wuttu. Awa gomЙ—inee Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en dennda-ngal hara on senndaali Й“e, wata on wi'u : ""ReweteeЙ—i Й—in ko tati"", haЙ—itee gaay e kan haala fenaande ; ko Й—um Й“uri moЖґЖґannde on aduna e laakara. Anndee pellet, Alla ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto, SeniiЙ—o gaay e kafideede e Й“iЙ—Й—o ! Ko O Galo. Ko Kanko Woodani laamateeri kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni e majji. Alla Yonii HoolorЙ—o."
  4,172,"Mema-sella Й“iЙ—Й—o Maryama on salataa o haЙ—itaaki nde o laatotoo jeyaaЙ—o Alla, wanaa Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“e ЖЃaЙ—tinani mo Й“en. Honno jogitorton Iisaa rewe- teeЙ—o ?! Ko honno sirkooЙ“e Й“en kadi jogitorta Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en reweteeЙ—i ?! Kala non nefinanii- Й—o rewugol Alla ngol, o townitanii Й—um, pellet, Alla MooЙ“itoyay Й“e denndaangal faade ka Makko Г‘alnde Darngal, O YoЙ“ita kala e ko hanndi kon."
  4,173,"Si tawii ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e NulaaЙ“e Makko Й“en, Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe e hoore no sari'a on yami- yamriri non, arma O Okka Й“e baraaji golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en O ЖЃeydana Й“e immorde e ЖЃural Makko ngal. ЖЃeya townitiiЙ“e e rewugol Mo Й—oftoo Mo, O Leptay Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e, Й“e heЙ“oytaa gaanin Alla, giЙ—o nafoowo Й“e, wanaa ballo duГ±anoowo Й“e lorra."
  4,174,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! GomЙ—ii hujja arii e mooЙ—on immorde ka Joomi mon ; on le ko Muhammadu (jom kisiyee), Men Jippinii e mooЙ—on ndaygu Й“anngu ngu ; ngun woni ndee Al Qur'aanaare."
  4,175,"Si tawii ko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e jogitii Alquraana Jippinaande nden e Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on, arma Alla Yumee Й“e, O Naada Й“e Aljanna, O ЖЃeydana Й“e njoЙ“di e darja, O Fewnira Й“e laawol focciingol ; ngol woni laawol Aljanna ngol."
  4,176,"HiЙ“e faltino maa an NulaaЙ—o fii rona-jala -ko on woni maayЙ—o mo accaa baaba e Й“iЙ—Й—o- Maaku : ""Alla no ЖЃannginannde on Г±aawoore mun : si goЙ—Й—o maayii o accaali baaba e Й“iЙ—Й—o, hara himo mari banndiraawo debbo neene gooto maa baaba gooto, hino woodani on banndiraawo makko geЙ“al feccere jawdi ndin- gorko neene gootoojo maayЙ—o on maa baaba gootoojo makko ronata si owondaa e ronoowo-. Si banndiraaЙ“e rewЙ“e maayЙ—o on laatike Й—iЙ—o maa ko Й“uri, Й“e roniday tataЙ“e Й—iЙ—i. Si neene gootooЙ“e maa baaba gootooЙ“e maayЙ—o on jillii worЙ“e e rewЙ“e, gorko on ronay geЙ“al rewЙ“e Й—iЙ—o. Alla no ЖЃannginannde on Г±aawoore rona-jala e woЙ—Й“e goo ka ndonndi, fii wata fii mun majjitor on. Alla Laatike AnnduЙ—o kala huunde""."
